## Implementation Details:

This is a Next.js App Router project (using the app directory), so the Analytics component was added to the root layout file (src/app/layout.tsx) as required.

The component is placed at the end of the body tag, following the same pattern as the existing SpeedInsights component. This ensures analytics tracking is properly initialized for all pages in the application.

